                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "{ \\widehat { f } } ( \\xi )"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "is also compactly supported. "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "2) Prove the following classical interior Schauder estimates: "
                            }
